GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CCABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 27th June, 1970.
6th Asadha, 1892.
The undersigned is directed to state that with offect
from the afternoon of June 26, 1970,
(i) Dr. S. Chandrasekhar relinquished the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Health and
Family Plahning, and Works, Housing & Urban
Development;
(ii) Dr. (Smt.) Phulrenu Guha relinquished the office
of Minister of State in the Ministry of Law and in
the Department of Social Welfare;
(iii) Shrimati Jahanara Jaipal Singh relinquished the
office of Deputy Minister in the Ministry of
Education & Youth Services.
